###Introduction

This is a c++ scribe client for zipkin.

###Requirements

    g++
    boost
    thrift

Installing thrift

    git clone git@github.com:apache/thrift.git
    ./configure --prefix=/usr/local
    make
    make install
    
Adding /usr/local to ldconfig path

    # echo "/usr/local/lib" >> /etc/ld.so.conf
    # ldconfig

Run sofa scribe demo

    make
    ./main
    